🌐 HTML Book Themed Website 📚
This project is a University project for the Hypertext & Hypermedia course. It aims to create a personal website focused on the books theme using HTML and CSS.

🚀 Features:
Custom Layout: Simple yet effective website design with HTML and CSS.
Book-Themed Content: The website is centered around books, ideal for showcasing book collections, recommendations, or reviews.
Responsive Design: Optimized for different screen sizes.

📦 Installation
Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/MaksPek03/HTMLPage.git
cd HTMLPage

Open the Website:
After cloning, simply open the index.html file in any browser to view the website.
open index.html  # Or double-click the file to open in your browser
